title: ON THE ROAD WITH PC  Season 2 Episode 4
description:
Back in France, Paul Cesar Distinguin is becoming a man now, graduating high school, receiving his diploma and planning big expectations for the next upcoming season. 
He's already working on his winter program. He will travel to Tahiti and Australia to contest all the pro-events there, and later will follow the entire European tour. 
Enjoy this nice edit filmed at the end of the summer and included bonus, his win at the VQS MULLET FISH Hossegor. 


- Music -

Song: "Never Trust a Bikey if He Don't Drink Beer"
Artist: Ozzie Wright
Release: Ozzy Wrongs Ukulele Songs
